Name: Bunny's Trail
About the game: Do you have good memory? Observe the scene for a few seconds and memorize the position of the items. Avoid obstacles and collect all carrots. About the game Bunny's Trail is a colorful 3D Puzzle game, navigate a little rabbit and go through the safe path to collect all the hidden carrots. Enjoy this cute and relaxing game for all ages. Features 50 Levels Simple Controls Original soundtracks Partial Controller Support Cute and colorful graphics
